{"arkId":"cl010359336","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010359336","modified ":"2025-11-22","title":"vase","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Ancien titre","value":"Copie de la pat\u00e8re de la chasse (AO 17 208)"},{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"vase"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : Bronze r\u00e9cent II (copie) (-1400 - -1200)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-1400,"endYear":-1200,"imprecision":"","text":"Bronze r\u00e9cent II","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"AO 17208 BIS","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"coupe\r\n\r\nPr\u00e9cision sur l\u0027objet : Copie. Coupe \u00e0 profil car\u00e9n\u00e9 et de forme sph\u00e9rique. Une file de 4 bouquetins marche sur la petite frise. Sur la grande frise un homme accompagn\u00e9 par 2 chiens, du haut de son char, tir\u00e9 par 2 chevaux, chasse une antilope et des taureaux sauvages fuyants au galop volant. Les guides sont nou\u00e9es autour de la taille du chasseur qui a ainsi les 2 mains libres pour tendre l\u0027arc. Un carquois rempli de fl\u00e8ches est presque enti\u00e8rement cach\u00e9 derri\u00e8re son dos. Un autre carquois est fix\u00e9 obliquement sur le c\u00f4t\u00e9 ext\u00e9rieur du char.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,5","displayDimension":"3,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"18,4","displayDimension":"18,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : r\u00e9sine (dor\u00e9, proc